These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-4-1::.
7 different games are played: snooker, scrabble, billiard, bridge, monopoly, backgammon, mah-jongg
The people have 7 different jobs:  accountant, dressmaker, electrician, lawyer, mechanic, police-officer, scientist
House: craftsman, palace, art-deco, futuristic, ranch-style, townhouse, cape-cod
The people have 7 different hobbies: photography, baking, sudoku, card-games, camping, writing, fishing
 1. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left or right of the townhouse house##3
 2. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the mechanic is the person who's hobby is writing##1
 4. the person playing snooker is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the person who's hobby is photography is the art-deco house##1
 6. the craftsman house is the person playing backgammon##1
 7. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left or right of the accountant##3
 8. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left or right of the person playing mah-jongg##3
 9. the person who's hobby is fishing is in an odd position##4
10. the scientist is on the left or right of the craftsman house##3
11. the police-officer is the person playing billiard##1
12. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left or right of the person playing bridge##3
13. the mechanic is on the right of the dressmaker##1
14. the craftsman house is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
15. the person playing billiard is between the accountant and the person who's hobby is camping##2
16. the police-officer is on the left of the electrician##1
17. the person playing bridge is the person who's hobby is camping##1
18. the lawyer is on the far left or far right##3
19. the police-officer is on the left or right of the accountant##3
20. the police-officer is the person playing billiard##1
21. the cape-cod house is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
22. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
23. the ranch-style house is on the left or right of the accountant##3
24. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far left or far right##3
25. the mechanic is on the right of the palace house##1
26. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the accountant##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |       3        |       4       |     5      |     6      |      7       |
| Game        | scrabble | backgammon     | billiard           | bridge          | monopoly  | mah-jongg | snooker         |
